Walk to End Alzheimer's Kick-Off Party Location: The Abbey, Orlando FL Join MC Ybeth Bruzual of News 13 at the 2015 Orlando Walk to End Alzheimer’s FREE KICK-OFF PARTY! Baby Boogie Bash: Amaya Papaya’s Super Hero 6th Birthday Party Location: Amaya Papaya, Casselberry FL The Baby Boogie Bash (East Coast) is a dance party for kids 0-7 years old featuring disco lights and music from the 80’s, 90’s, and today. No Nursery Rhymes, just real jams (appropriate of course) that will get your feet moving and body grooving. We offer the Baby Boogie Bash at Amaya Papaya 7 times a year. Each event is themed to match a corresponding holiday throughout the year and then eclectically themed during our summer party series culminating with our annual Birthday Party! For more information on this baby boogie bash, email: info@amayapapaya.com. See you there! View Map & Details

National House of Hope Conference - Katherine Ruonala Location: Faith Assembly, Orlando FL You’re invited to the National House of Hope Conference! She will be speaking and ministering at 7:00 p.m. on both nights at Faith Assembly Church (Michigan Street location). Registration is FREE. Visit, House of Hope Orlando to reserve your seat today!
